body: Hey guys! I need some help with something. I just downloaded a soundboard for TS, but when I try to activate it, I get this. This is the website for the soundboard I got (also the one linked to on TS' website). https://frie.se/ts3sb/

title: Soundboard help.

replies.body: Yeah, when you try to download the newest version it won't load as a plugin. You have to go and download one of the older versions of the soundboard. Google "Teamspeak Old Soundboard." It should come out.
replies.body_tagged: Yeah, when you try to download the newest version it won't load as a plugin. You have to go and download one of the older versions of the soundboard. Google "Teamspeak Old Soundboard." It should come out.

replies.body:
Ok, thank you! Let me try it out!
